com/news/gaming-news/battlefield-2042-gets-hourglass-rework-and-squad-orders-in-update-5-2-0-3475575">更改了沙漏地图的大片区域</a>，以便“保持战斗重点，同时有更多机会保护自己”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/path-of-exile-2-dev-says-blizzard-learned-hard-lessons-with-diablo-4-3475624">《流亡之路 2》开发者称暴雪从《暗黑破坏神 4》中吸取了“惨痛的教训”，该游戏</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
