西妮德·奥康纳在去世前两周警告粉丝，她受到“暴力”跟踪者的骚扰https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-warned-fans-of-violent-stalker-two-weeks-before-death-3475615?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sinead-oconnor-warned-暴力跟踪者死前两周的粉丝Hollie GeraghtyMon, 31 Jul 2023 10:45:40 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3475615 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sinead-oconnor-warns-of-stalker.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sinead-oconnor-warns-of-stalker.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sinead-oconnor-warns-of-stalker-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sinead-oconnor-warns-of-stalker-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sinead-oconnor-warns-of-stalker-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sinead-oconnor-warns-of-stalker-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sinead-oconnor-warns-of-stalker-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位爱尔兰歌手告诉歌迷不要与任何自称是她的人接触</p><p>西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinéad O&#39;Connor) 的帖子警告粉丝，她在死亡事件首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-warned-fans-of-violent-stalker-two-weeks-before-death-3475615">的两周前，遭到了“暴力”跟踪者的骚扰</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sinead-oconnor-warns-of-stalker.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sinead-oconnor-warns-of-stalker.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sinead-oconnor-warns-of-stalker-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sinead-oconnor-warns-of-stalker-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sinead-oconnor-warns-of-stalker-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sinead-oconnor-warns-of-stalker-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sinead-oconnor-warns-of-stalker-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sinead-oconnor">西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinéad O&#39;Connor)</a>告诉粉丝，她在去世前两周遭到“暴力”跟踪者的骚扰。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/sinead-oconnor-obituary-3473864">Sinéad O&#39;Connor，1966-2023：一位正直、强烈和诚实的艺术家</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位标志性的爱尔兰音乐家和活动家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies-aged-56-3473863">上周</a>（7 月 26 日） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-was-found-unresponsive-at-home-police-say-3474196">被发现在伦敦家中失去知觉</a>后去世，享年 56 岁。她在现场被宣布死亡，她的死亡并未被视为可疑。</p><p>奥康纳在 7 月 15 日的一条推文中写道：“还有一个跟踪者。女性。暴力：再说一次，在没有询问我的管理层的情况下，切勿与任何声称认识我的人接触。”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">另外还有一名跟踪狂。女性。暴力：再次强调，在没有询问我的管理层的情况下，切勿与任何声称认识我的人接触。</p><p> — Sinead Marie-Bernarde Aoibheann O&#39;Connor (@786OmShahid) <a href="https://twitter.com/786OmShahid/status/1680259274574901248?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 7 月 15 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>在另一条推文中，奥康纳表示，她之前曾与“一名极度不安的男性性掠夺者”打过交道，该男子“通过自称是我的男朋友，在我的推特页面上培养了脆弱的女性粉丝”。她补充道：“再次强调，永远不要与任何自称是任何人的人交往。那里有大量的恶魔。不管怎样，我还是单身； ）”。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">另外警告一下，之前有一位极度不安的男性性掠夺者在推特上假装是我：请不要与任何自称是名人的人交往，除非确认他们的身份。这可以通过联系他们的管理层来实现</p><p>— Sinead Marie-Bernarde Aoibheann O&#39;Connor (@786OmShahid) <a href="https://twitter.com/786OmShahid/status/1680258607462469632?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 7 月 15 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-revealed-devastating-impact-of-sons-death-in-final-social-media-post-3474211">然而，这位歌手的最后一篇社交媒体帖子揭示了她儿子去年去世的毁灭性影响</a>。</p><p>奥康纳 17 岁的儿子谢恩 (Shane) 在基尔代尔郡纽布里奇<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-pays-tribute-to-17-year-old-son-following-his-death-3132870">失踪后于 2022 年 1 月自杀身亡</a>。随后，为了“她自己的健康和福祉”，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-cancels-all-gigs-in-2022-for-her-own-health-and-wellbeing-3250458">取消了当年的所有演出</a>。</p><p>奥康纳在<a href="https://twitter.com/786omshahid/status/1680906340451876864?s=46&amp;t=I39FXC_3djy_bwC-EDjNgA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">帖子</a>中写道：“从那时起，我就以不死的夜间生物的身份生活。他是我一生的挚爱，我灵魂的灯。我们是一个灵魂，分成两半。他是唯一一个无条件地爱我的人。没有他，我就迷失在中阴了。”</p><p>这位歌手当时在社交媒体上宣布了自己的去世，他写道：“我美丽的儿子内维姆·内斯塔·阿里·肖恩·奥康纳，我生命中的光明，决定今天结束他在尘世的挣扎，现在与上帝在一起。愿他安息，愿没有人效仿他。我的宝贝。我真的很爱你。请保持安静。”</p><p>自上周这位爱尔兰音乐偶像去世以来，音乐界一直在向她致敬， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sinead-oconnor-fans-gather-to-sing-nothing-compares-2-u-at-dublin-tribute-3475498">本周歌迷们聚集在都柏林演唱《Nothing Compares 2 U》</a> 。</p><p>这位艺术家最著名的歌曲最初是由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/prince">Prince</a>为他的副业项目《The Family》创作和创作的，最近在一些演出中为这位歌手表演了歌曲。 </p><figure id="attachment_3473874" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3473874" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3473874" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3473874" class="wp-caption-text">荷兰 – 1 月 1 日：Sinead O&#39;CONNOR 的照片（摄影：Michel Linssen/Redferns）</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink">P!nk</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brandi-carlile">Brandi Carlile</a>在最近的一场演出中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pnk-and-brandi-carlile-cover-nothing-compares-2-u-in-tribute-to-sinead-oconnor-3474214">翻唱了《Nothing Compares 2 U》</a> ，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fall-out-boy">Fall Out Boy</a>也在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-fall-out-boy-cover-nothing-compares-2-u-in-tribute-to-sinead-oconnor-3474325">一场演出中翻唱了这首歌。</a>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighers-and-alanis-morissette-honour-sinead-oconnor-with-mandinka-cover-3475206">Foo Fighters 和 Alanis Morissette</a>在本周末的一个音乐节上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighers-and-alanis-morissette-honour-sinead-oconnor-with-mandinka-cover-3475206">表演了“Mandinka”</a> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies-aged-56-3473863">其他在她去世后迅速表达哀悼的艺术家</a>包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/garbage">Garbage</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-corgan">Billy Corgan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-stipe">Michael Stipe</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-t">Ice-T 等</a>。</p><p>奥康纳<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-was-working-on-a-new-album-before-her-death-3474286">透露，她去世前正在制作一张新专辑</a>。 “大家好，在阔别 23 年之后，最近搬回了伦敦。很高兴回到家:)很快就完成了我的专辑。明年初发布，”她在社交帖子中写道。</p><p>西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinéad O&#39;Connor) 的帖子警告粉丝，她在死亡事件首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-warned-fans-of-violent-stalker-two-weeks-before-death-3475615">的两周前，遭到了“暴力”跟踪者的骚扰</a>。</p> ;
